title.rendered: Marvellous First & Second Floor In Shanti Niketan Open For Booking

content.rendered:
Bookings are open for these exquisitely designed floors that face the northeast direction and have a beautiful park at the rear. These floors feature 4 well-appointed bedrooms with lavish connected baths, a Fully Loaded kitchen with Oven, Microwave, Hood, Hob, Dishwasher, Refrigerator, etc, wide balconies, stilt parking, and Exclusive Lifts.

♕Open For Booking
♕400 Yds
♕4BHK
♕First & Second Floor
♕Shanti Niketan
♕North-East Facing
♕Rear Park
♕Diplomatic Enclave
♕A+ Builder

Lalit Kaushik

Call On 98183-12077 For Site Visit

http://wa.me/919818312077

Follow @royalerealtorsindia on social media
Checkout Our Other Listings Here
ROYALE REALTORS INDIA
